      <title>由于高利率抑制销售，全球 ESG 债务增长缓慢</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/global-esg-debt-set-for-tepid-growth-as-high-rates-inhibit-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着借款人努力应对额外的标签成本、更高的利率和更严格的 ESG 审查，全球可持续债务市场可能会连续第三年难以再次突破高水位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/global-esg-debt-set-for-tepid-growth-as-high-rates-inhibit-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
